{"root":{"data":{"id":"dhg6ji8q8a00","created":1774880258025,"text":"嵌入式系统设计视角下的具身智能"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhg6jm0dbf40","created":1774880266227,"text":"1、研究动机"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhg6mb4y7t40","created":1774880477652,"text":"1.1 领域重要性"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhg6mubehv40","created":1774880519401,"text":"具身智能是AI与机器人、嵌入式系统的交叉前沿"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhg6mv2n0i00","created":1774880521048,"text":"具身智能是AI与机器人、嵌入式系统的交叉前沿"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhg6mw6vyu80","created":1774880523481,"text":"嵌入式系统承担感知、控制、推理、通信的实时闭环"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhg6mwwr72o0","created":1774880525045,"text":"典型应用：自主移动机器人、机械臂操作、仿生机器人、穿戴式AI"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhg6md9i3fs0","created":1774880482281,"text":"1.2 现有知识缺口"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhg6n774cgw0","created":1774880547440,"text":"复杂环境下的实时感知与运动控制协同不足"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhg6n7o8oo80","created":1774880548475,"text":"嵌入式算力有限与具身大模型（如VLA、RT-2）推理延迟的矛盾"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhg6n7qpy6g0","created":1774880548625,"text":"多模态（视觉、力觉、触觉）传感器融合在低功耗平台上的效率问题"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhg6n7tvcls0","created":1774880548816,"text":"长期自主运行中的能量管理与适应性学习缺乏系统级方案"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhg6n7x6fm80","created":1774880549016,"text":"具身智能的安全性（物理安全、对抗攻击）在嵌入式实现中几乎空白题"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhg6o4n42bc0","created":1774880620241,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhg6o55hf140","created":1774880621352,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhg6o581w6g0","created":1774880621507,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}